title: Lifetime-Flowers in the Attic [2014]
description:
Lifetime-Flowers in the Attic (2014) 

Air Date: 18 Jan 2014

Summary: Based on V.C. Andrews' controversial, cult classic book, Flowers in the Attic tells the story of the Dollanganger kids who, after the unexpected death of their father, are convinced to stay hidden in the attic of their ruthless Grandmother.
